Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Take this amazing opportunity at Smithfield Shopping Village  with their existing operators and their current customer base.

If you are looking for a new premises or and second site then look now further as we have the perfect location. 

Our current tenancy mix comprises of the following medical Practice, F45 Gym, Green Grocer, Hairs & Makeup, Psychologist, Real Estate offices, Eat Street Café, Blossom Bakery , Pizzeria and Thai takeaway.

We are looking for Allied Health Professionals ranging from but not limited to Physio, Chiropractor and Dentist.


PLEASE NOTE: All tenancies are currently leased however there will be vacancies in the coming months. Please contact the agent to find out more or register your interest. 

Property Features
•	Sizes ranging from 69m2 – 129m2
•	Shop 11 - Size 129sqm
•	Shop 12D - Size 69sqm
•	Excellent exposure & signage opportunities 
•	Full glass frontage
•	Suitable for Medical, retail or office use
•	Concrete floors
•	48 car parks on site plus ample on street parking
•	Large Residential catchment area 

For further information or arrange an inspection, please contact Joanne Brown from CBRE on 0412 082 102.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Smithfield Shopping Village is strategically located on a prominent corner on the recently opened Smithfield Village Drive which is a new thoroughfare linking Yorkeys through to Trinity Beach as well as access to the Bruce Highway. Opposite a very busy Childcare Centre and well placed to Secondary and Primary Schools as well as being situated in the centre of the residential growth corridor of the Northern Beaches.

PLEASE NOTE: All tenancies are currently leased however there will be vacancies in the coming months. Please contact the agent to find out more or register your interest. 


PROPERTY FEATURES:
+ Glazed shop fronts with single framed doors, larger shops  
   double doors
+ Cassette air conditioning
+ Internal toilet and kitchenette with cold water to most shops
+ Covered walkways for access convenience
+ Excellent exposure and signage
+ Trade waste / grease trap access to most shops
+ Front and rear entry to larger shops
+ 48 on site car parks plus a further 10 street car parks

For further information, please contact Joanne Brown from CBRE on 0412 082 102.
